interpretation: The Fast-Forward Button emoji represents the idea of moving quickly towards your goals and leaving behind the past. It is a symbol of progress, urgency, and taking action. This card encourages you to push forward and not get stuck in the past, to seize opportunities and move towards your desired outcome. It may also suggest the need to speed up your pace or to focus on efficiency in order to achieve your goals. The Fast-Forward Button reminds you that time is valuable and that it's important to make the most of it. This card can also indicate a need to embrace change and to adapt to new circumstances. It's time to move forward with confidence and determination.
